<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Dec 2021 08:26:20 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Microsoft「踩地雷」醜毛衣　一日內全數售罄</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/03/microsoft-is-selling-ugly-windows-sweaters-again-and-this-time-its-minesweeper/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=microsoft-is-selling-ugly-windows-sweaters-again-and-this-time-its-minesweeper</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 03 Dec 2021 08:25:57 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[microsoft]]></category><category><![CDATA[Ugly Sweater]]></category><category><![CDATA[踩地雷]]></category><category><![CDATA[醜毛衣]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073867</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 由去年開始，聖誕節前後都會推出一款醜陋毛衣（Ugly Sweater），而今年推出的毛衣主 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft 由去年開始，聖誕節前後都會推出一款醜陋毛衣（Ugly Sweater），而今年推出的毛衣主題是 Microsoft 的經典遊戲「踩地雷」。毛衣一經發售便受到瘋搶，現時所有尺寸已經售罄，第二批貨需要等到 12 月中。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/A966232C-0FFF-49AA-8DA7-451F5BCFC90E-694x461.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/A966232C-0FFF-49AA-8DA7-451F5BCFC90E-694x461.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/A966232C-0FFF-49AA-8DA7-451F5BCFC90E-768x510.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/A966232C-0FFF-49AA-8DA7-451F5BCFC90E.jpeg 1216w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073872" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499-694x327.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="327" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499-694x327.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499-1280x603.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499-768x362.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499-1536x723.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499-2048x964.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/BA714443-09A9-4BDC-BE7D-C35982E96499.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今年是 Microsoft 第二次推出醜陋毛衣，其主要的設計靈感是過去 Windows 的 Logo 或經典元素。例如去年曾推出一款「看起來很幽默」的小畫家應用程式服裝，毛衣就有如用小畫家設計的一樣；而今年則是將《踩地雷》作為其主題，整個踩地雷的關卡形狀被設計成聖誕樹，還將按鈕、炸彈布置成跟雪花一模一樣。毛衣顯示了 Windows 舊款的介面風格，看到最經典的波浪型 Windows 懷舊感爆棚，右上角還設計最小化窗口或退出遊戲，並在秒數和剩餘炸彈欄上寫著「1990」和「2021」這兩個數字，而 1990 年其實是微軟「踩地雷」問世那年。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3B42AEB8-5CA2-4A95-8BC3-8FF39F2DE73A-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3B42AEB8-5CA2-4A95-8BC3-8FF39F2DE73A-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3B42AEB8-5CA2-4A95-8BC3-8FF39F2DE73A-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3B42AEB8-5CA2-4A95-8BC3-8FF39F2DE73A-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3B42AEB8-5CA2-4A95-8BC3-8FF39F2DE73A-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/3B42AEB8-5CA2-4A95-8BC3-8FF39F2DE73A.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/72EEFF03-2377-4027-8BF1-7C6C9F70EFA6-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/72EEFF03-2377-4027-8BF1-7C6C9F70EFA6-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/72EEFF03-2377-4027-8BF1-7C6C9F70EFA6-900x900.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/72EEFF03-2377-4027-8BF1-7C6C9F70EFA6-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/72EEFF03-2377-4027-8BF1-7C6C9F70EFA6-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/72EEFF03-2377-4027-8BF1-7C6C9F70EFA6.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今年毛衣的售價定為 74.99 美元（約港幣 584 元），比去年貴了 5 美元（約港幣 39 元）。據稱毛衣的一部份收益將會捐給慈善團體，現時已捐了 10 萬美元給一個名為 AbleGamers 的慈善機構，以幫助殘疾遊戲玩家。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Whatchu know about Minesweeper? <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/UglyChristmasSweater?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#UglyChristmasSweater</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/WindowsUglySweater?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#WindowsUglySweater</a> <a href="https://t.co/nWnn42uyw2">pic.twitter.com/nWnn42uyw2</a></p><p>&mdash; Marques Brownlee (@MKBHD) <a href="https://twitter.com/MKBHD/status/1465452689974861826?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 29, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/tldr/2021/11/30/22810369/microsoft-ugly-windows-sweater-party-minesweeper">THE VERGE</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
